0.1.7.name: wordpress/ywa-yahoo-web-analytics
0.1.7.description:
This plugin will add tracking features to your wordpress blog without have to know any PHP, edit code, or cut and paste tracking code to footers. Also, if you change or update themes, you will not have to remember to update tracking code.

Features

  • Enter all settings through admin screen
  • Tracks all pages
  • Captures logged in status of users
  • Captures internal search terms
  • Captures number of search results
  • Captures 404 data
  • Ability to track/not track Administrators
  • Tracks Comments as Actions
